caller_intent: Stephen Killes is seeking an alternate insurance quote (specifically from Utica) after the previous Auto Owners quote disappeared, and he wants assurance that the new quote won't disappear again.
resolution_steps: Heather confirms that Auto Owners is a top carrier and acknowledges the issue with the missing quote.
She checks the Utica quote and agrees to send a revised version.
Heather assures Stephen she will revise and resend the correct quote.
knowledge_required: Knowledge of insurance carriers (Auto Owners, Utica) and their pricing structures.
Ability to retrieve and resend quotes via email.
Understanding of customer concerns about quote reliability.
systems_referenced: Email system (mention of emails disappearing and needing to resend).
summary: Stephen Killes requested an alternate insurance quote after the Auto Owners quote disappeared. Heather confirmed Auto Owners' reliability, checked the Utica quote, and agreed to send a revised version. The call concluded with Heather committing to resend the correct information.
